OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FWarning: This article contains
OL,8,Fexpletives and details of a
OL,9,Fdistressing nature
OL,11,FA man has pleaded guilty to the
OL,12,Freligiously-aggravated rape and
OL,13,Fassault of a Sikh woman in Walsall who
OL,14,Fhe wrongly believed to be Muslim.
OL,16,FJohn Ashby, who's 32 and of no fixed
OL,17,Fabode, attacked the victim after
OL,18,Ftravelling on the same bus as her. He
OL,19,Ffollowed her home and entered while
OL,20,Fshe was upstairs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
