OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FEarlier today the trial at Birmingham
OL,8,FCrown Court was disrupted after a
OL,9,Fmember of the public walked up to the
OL,10,Fdock and shouted verbal abuse.
OL,12,FCCTV footage from the 25th October
OL,13,F2025 showed Ashby getting off the same
OL,14,Fbus as the woman.
OL,16,FHe followed her for around ten
OL,17,Fminutes, with some distance between
OL,18,Fthem. She did not know she was being
OL,19,Ffollowed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FHe was then seen loitering outside her
OL,8,Fhouse, where he found a stick around a
OL,9,Fmetre and a half long, which he put in
OL,10,Fhis clothes. CCTV then picked up a
OL,11,Fscream from inside the woman's house.
OL,13,FExtracts from body-worn police footage
OL,14,Fshowing the woman, who cannot be
OL,15,Fidentified, were played to a jury of
OL,16,Fsix men and six women today, during
OL,17,Fwhich the victim was comforted by a
OL,18,Ffemale officer, and said her attacker
OL,19,Fhad called her a "bloody Muslim bitch".
OL,26,@{D@ROU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
