CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FThe woman, said by witnesses to have
OL,8,Fbeen hysterical while repeatedly
OL,9,Fscreaming, told police she had been
OL,10,Fraped in a bathroom by the intruder,
OL,11,Fwho was armed with a stick he found
OL,12,Foutside, and claimed to be a "British
OL,13,Fmaster".
OL,15,F"I am not a Muslim, I am a Sikh"
OL,17,FIn a video interview played to the
OL,18,Fcourt, the victim told police:
OL,20,F"He had a stick in his hand. I said
OL,21,F'who are you' and I started screaming.
OL,26,@tD@^OUuD@GO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,F"He switched off the light. He said 'I
OL,8,Fjust want fun with you'. He said 'you
OL,9,Fare a f****** Muslim bitch, I said I
OL,10,Fam not a Muslim, I am a Sikh."
OL,12,FThe woman also told police the man was
OL,13,Finitially aggressive and had
OL,14,Fcontinuously verbally abused her but
OL,15,Fthen became calm.
OL,17,FAs the video interview was being
OL,18,Fplayed to the jury, a man left the
OL,19,Fpublic gallery and approached the
OL,20,Fglass-fronted dock and swore at Ashby.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
