PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FThe man told Ashby "you need to sort
OL,8,Fyour shit out".
OL,10,FAshby responded by telling the man to
OL,11,F"get the f*** out of my face" and also
OL,12,Fshouted at another member of the
OL,13,Fpublic who had remained seated in the
OL,14,Fpublic gallery.
OL,16,FTrial judge Mr Justice Pepperall
OL,17,Fadjourned the case, sending the jury
OL,18,Faway for a lunch break.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@NO]sD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
