OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe trial then resumed without Ashby
OL,13,Fin the dock.
OL,15,FThe judge instructed the jury to
OL,16,Fignore the "rather ugly" and
OL,17,F"intemperate exchange" involving Ashby
OL,18,Fand a member of the public, saying:
OL,19,F"It should not have happened."
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@XO]yD@AOUyD@VO]{D@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
