OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FThe judge added: "Put that out of your
OL,8,Fmind ` it's not evidence in this case."
OL,10,FAddressing Ashby's absence from the
OL,11,Fcourtroom, the judge said:
OL,13,F"You will notice that the dock is
OL,14,Fempty." Mr Ashby has voluntarily
OL,15,Fchosen to exercise his right not come
OL,16,Fup in to the courtroom this afternoon.
OL,17,FPlease do not speculate further as to
OL,18,Fwhy he is not here. It's the evidence
OL,19,Fyou need to focus on."
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@gO]uD@AOUvD@GOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
