OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FAshby changed his pleas to guilty of
OL,8,Frape, intentional strangulation,
OL,9,Frobbery as he stole jewellery and a
OL,10,Fmobile phone as he left the house, and
OL,11,Fracially-aggravated assault.
OL,13,FThe judge said "He should be under no
OL,14,Fillusion that a life sentence is the
OL,15,Fright sentence in this case.
OL,17,F"It seems to be that anybody who
OL,18,Fcommits these offences in these
OL,19,Fcircumstances is a very dangerous
OL,20,Findividual."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
