OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FAshby will be sentenced on 24th April.
OL,9,F"The clear danger this perpetrator
OL,10,Fposes"
OL,12,FThe charity Sikh Women's Aid says it
OL,13,Fwelcomes the guilty plea entered in
OL,14,Fthe case.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
