PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FIt said a series of attacks between
OL,8,FAugust and October 2025 where women
OL,9,Fwere raped and others racially
OL,10,Ftargeted led to fear across many Sikh
OL,11,FPunjabi communities across the
OL,12,FMidlands and the UK, and says many
OL,13,Fwomen changed their daily routines as
OL,14,Fa result.
OL,16,FIt said their thoughts "remain firmly
OL,17,Fwith the survivor at the centre of
OL,18,Fthis case. Her courage and resilience
OL,19,Fin seeking justice following such a
OL,20,Fhorrific ordeal must be recognised".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
