PN,37612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776841517
OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,FChair, Sukhvinder Kaur said:
OL,9,F"The defendant chose to proceed to
OL,10,Ftrial, prolonging proceedings and
OL,11,Fcontributing to the ongoing trauma
OL,12,Fexperienced by the victim, only to
OL,13,Fchange his plea partway through.
OL,15,F"This reflects wider concerns about
OL,16,Fhow perpetrators are able to navigate
OL,17,Fthe system in ways that can compound
OL,18,Fharm for survivors.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
