OL,3,CRapist changes pleas to guilty after
OL,4,Cattack on Sikh woman he thought was
OL,5,CMuslim
OL,7,F"We now look to the sentencing hearing
OL,8,Fon Friday and expect that it reflects
OL,9,Fthe severity of the harm caused and
OL,10,Fthe clear danger this perpetrator
OL,11,Fposes".
